elements.name: User should add product to cart successfully

steps.name: I mouse hover on Desktop tab and Click
I click on Show All Desktop
I click on Sort By Position Name: A to Z
I select product HP LP3065
I should navigate to product page and should see text HP LP3065
I select delivery date 2023-11-30
I click on Add to Cart
I should see message Success: You have added HP LP3065 to your shopping cart!
I click on link shopping cart display into success message
I should see text Shopping Cart
I click on currency tab
I change currency to £ sterling
I should see text HP LP3065
I should see the Delivery Date 2023-11-30
I should see the model Product21
I shouldsee total price is £74.73

Click on Show All Laptops & Notebooks

elements.name: User should place the order successfully

steps.name: I Mouse hover on Laptops & Notebooks Tab and click
I Click on Show All Laptops & Notebooks
I Select Sort By Price (High > Low)
I Select Product MacBook
I should see Product name MacBook
I Click on Add To Cart button
I should see message Success: You have added MacBook to your shopping cart!
I click on link shopping cart display into success message
I click on currency tab
I change currency to £ sterling
I should see Shopping Cart
I should see Product name is MacBook
I Change Quantity to 2
I click on Update tab
I should see message Success: You have modified your shopping cart!
I should see the updated price £737.45
I click on Checkout button
I should see text Checkout
I should see text New Customer
I click on Guest Checkout radio button
I click on Continue tab
I fill all the mandatory details
I click on Continue
I enter Comments about order into text field
